    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Speech
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    A Sustainable Recovery for People and Planet
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">COP26 President Alok Sharma at 'A Sustainable Recovery for People and Planet', part of the 2020 Annual Meetings of the International Monetary Fund (IMF) and the Board of Governors of the World Bank Group (WBG) </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 14 October 2020
</div>

      <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata__other">
        <dl data-module="track-click">
